You are on Chester Street.

You can go in, east or west.
You are outside Your House on a side road near the city centre, that runs from East to West.

In the gutter a pigeon is joyfully pecking at the remains of a discarded KFC. It's a crisp cold day, in the distance you can hear carol singing..

> x pigeon

> x pigeon

A grey city pigeon with a grumpy demeanour
> x KFC

> x KFC

It's the forsaken remains of a KFC meal, a 'mighty bucket for one' by the looks of it. Probably discarded last night by someone staggering home from the Cross Keys Inn
> talk to pigeon

> talk to pigeon

The pigeon replies;  "My Name's Jon, and I'm a fucking pigeon."
> ask Jon about KFC

> ask Jon about KFC

"It's my KFC, fuck you."
> take KFC

> take KFC

You stoop down to pick it up but the pigeon exclaims, "It's my KFC! Fuck off!". The murderous glint in the pigeon's eye persuades you to leave the KFC on the ground.
> ask Jon about Christmas

> ask Jon about Christmas

The Pigeon says " Here's a good game...

