You are in a Butcher's Shop.
You can see a Butcher's Delivery Bike, a Butcher and The Last Turkey In The Shop.

You can go east.
You part the red strip door blind and enter the butcher's shop, the air inside has a tang of iron and bleach. Like every other shop late on Christmas eve the counters have been stripped nearly bare of produce.

> x turkey

> x turkey

A recently deceased turkey, (joined the choir invisible, shuffled off his mortal coil... etc).

It's the last one in the shop, it's small but perfectly formed, just the job.

> x butcher

> x butcher

A young man in his twenties, you recognise him as Robin, the son of the owner Mr U'blind. He looks tired and stressed.

He's wearing butcher's white overalls with smears of blood, and white rubber boots also smeared with blood.
> x bike

> x bike

A black framed delivery bike, with a smaller wheel at the front than at the back to make space for a large wicker basket, which is full of crates and parcels of greaseproof paper tied with string. You try to turn the peddles but they are very stiff.
> talk to Robin

> talk to Robin

"Hello" says the Butcher, "Been one hell of a day, been rushed off my feet since 7 o'clock this morning. I've still got my deliveries to do before I can call it a day, but my bike is seized up"
> ask Robin about turkey

> ask Robin about turkey

Yep its the last one, a bit smaller than the rest, but free range, organic, spoilt, Farmer Bell treats them like his children, weeps like a child when December comes round. I can't give it away for free, Dad will kill me!
> ask Robin about bike

> ask Robin about bike

"Damn thing is seized up, keep telling Dad I need a new one"
> ask Robin about oil

> ask Robin about oil

"That would help! But I don't have any."
> oil bike

> oil bike

You oil the bike's chain and running gear. After a few rotations of the pedals it's running smooth as silk.

The Butcher says "Thanks so much, you've saved Christmas for me and my customers, here take this.." He hands you the Turkey, gets on the bike and is off in a shot.
